mmdvm-core Licensing
====================

This crate is distributed under the GNU General Public License, version 2
or (at your option) any later version (GPL-2.0-or-later). This matches the
workspace-wide license choice for the kenwood project.

mmdvm-core is a sans-io Rust codec for the MMDVM ham-radio digital voice
modem protocol. It is a clean-room Rust reimplementation of the protocol
facts described in the reference C++ implementation MMDVMHost
(https://github.com/g4klx/MMDVMHost), which is distributed under
GPL-2.0-or-later for the files that inform this crate's derivation.

